													<!-- Content -->
													<div class="content">
														<div class="inner-content">
															<h5>Amartya Mehrotr...</h5>

																<p><p>Amartya Mehrotra, a B. Tech alumni from Sharda University describes his time at the University at par with the global universities. He says that the faculty helped him identify his strengths and helped him explore his true academic passions. The diverse range of international students on campus meant a real cultural experience for him.</p>

<p> </p></p>
														</div>
