												<li class="col-sm-3">
												<!-- Story Box -->
												<div class="story-box">
													<!-- Banner -->
													
													<div class="banner lazy" data-src="" onclick="redirectUrl('http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0WIbjwM3RUo')" style="background-image:url(https://img.youtube.com/vi/0WIbjwM3RUo/default.jpg)"></div>
													 <!-- <div class="banner">
														 <iframe width="80%" height="410"  frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
													 </div> -->
													
													<!-- /Banner -->
													<!-- Content -->
													<div class="content">
														<div class="inner-content">
															<h5>Nilisha Pokhrel</h5>

																<p><p style="text-align: justify;">Sharda University alumni are making a mark not only in India but also globally. Our alumni Ms. Nilisha Pokhrel, who is currently working as Postdoctoral Research Scholar at New England Biolabs Inc, Ipswich, MA, USA; expresses how choosing Sharda University helped her develop ample competence along with helping her in her professional journey in the field of biotechnology.</p></p>
														</div>
													  </div>
													<!-- /Content -->
												</div>
												<!-- /Story Box -->
											</li>
										
												<li class="col-sm-3">
												<!-- Story Box -->
												<div class="story-box">
													<!-- Banner -->
													
													<div class="banner lazy" data-src="" onclick="redirectUrl('http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EB32kWVrvsg')" style="background-image:url(https://img.youtube.com/vi/EB32kWVrvsg/default.jpg)"></div>
													 <!-- <div class="banner">
														 <iframe width="80%" height="410"  frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
													 </div> -->
													
													<!-- /Banner -->
													<!-- Content -->
													<div class="content">
														<div class="inner-content">
															<h5>Aditya Vardhan</h5>

																<p><p>Aditya Vardhan, a B.tech (Mechanical) student at Sharda University shares how the university offers a perfect blend of opportunities, challenges, and ambiance that has been a great learning experience and helped him explore new dimensions in his field of study.</p></p>
														</div>
													  </div>
													<!-- /Content -->
												</div>
												<!-- /Story Box -->
											</li>
										
												<li class="col-sm-3">
												<!-- Story Box -->
												<div class="story-box">
													<!-- Banner -->
													
													<div class="banner lazy" data-src="" onclick="redirectUrl('http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WrWXTvVKtgw')" style="background-image:url(https://img.youtube.com/vi/WrWXTvVKtgw/default.jpg)"></div>
													 <!-- <div class="banner">
														 <iframe width="80%" height="410"  frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
													 </div> -->
													
													<!-- /Banner -->
													<!-- Content -->
													<div class="content">
														<div class="inner-content">
															<h5>Khyolamo Kikon</h5>

																<p><p>Khyolamo Kikon, B.Tech (Civil Engineering) alumni of Sharda University shares that the inculcation of discipline at the university and the culture of value based education proved to be the keys that helped him open up his career path and helped him in his further studies. He says that he has a deep sense of gratitude for the knowledge and confidence the university imparted, and the friendships he formed during his time.</p></p>
														</div>
													  </div>
													<!-- /Content -->
												</div>
												<!-- /Story Box -->
											</li>
										
