													<!-- Banner -->
													
													<div class="banner lazy" data-src="" onclick="redirectUrl('http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z7K9fRCnAck')" style="background-image:url(https://img.youtube.com/vi/Z7K9fRCnAck/default.jpg)"></div>
													 <!-- <div class="banner">
														 <iframe width="80%" height="410"  frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
													 </div> -->
													
													<!-- /Banner -->
													<!-- Content -->
													<div class="content">
														<div class="inner-content">
															<h5>Atul Saxena</h5>

																<p><p>Mr. Atul Saxena, a B.Tech (ECE) alumni from Sharda University shares that his experience at Sharda has been a constant evolution of learning, perseverance and seizing opportunities. He shares that the faculty was really supportive and he is grateful for their guidance and support.</p></p>
